{"tid":1536274,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[急需文宣] 聽日起，戴口罩，直到贏","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:55:40.000Z","uid":63285,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9e4ca02c996f958b87aec8941610a263ca0005","tid":1536274,"uid":63285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:16:21.000Z","msg":"理由:<br />\n<br />\n由聽日起，全民戴口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534721\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534721</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣組可唔可以幫手宣傳，出文宣，罷工唔得，唔通戴個口罩又要驚? 和理非仲可以做咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60976eb50ab4b61112ab4da5f21881d0eeb30e6","tid":1536274,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:18:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\"